name: CLEANER FLOOR SURE GRIP 1 GAL
description: Sure Grip Floor Cleaner. Great for use on most floor surfaces including slate, ceramic, quarry, recycled PVS, terrazzo, concrete, wood, VCT and more. name: STRIPPER FLOOR LOW ODOR 1 GAL
